data.description:
Charming, 2 BR-2BA-2 Car garage with second living or office room, home  is nestled in the quaint town of Winnsboro. This Home is on a large corner lot. Enjoy morning coffees on the covered patio over looking the back yard, with a large storage building suitable for a shop-hobby room or she shed with windows and large slide up door. Spacious bedrooms with good size closets. Kitchen features tile counter tops and gas stove. Laminate wood flooring, original wood flooring in Living, hall and bedrooms. Home is in walking distance to shops and restaurants down town Winnsboro. Seller is making NO Repairs.
Preferred Title Company is Independence Title Co., Mesquite TX 75150
Agent is related to Seller.
